{"tid":1470229,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我是一名香港人，經過這一夜，我決定不再時時刻刻關注着。","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:12:24.000Z","uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"deaf2b8cf0e1437d296b8575a3fc12e4038499ec","tid":1470229,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"我是一名香港人，小中學都在香港就讀由於喜歡中醫因此來到內地完成我的本科學而接下來的九月我就要回香港繼續深造今天早上一看到這新聞讓我反思，如果我也面臨這處境，可以怎麼辦？沉默？反抗？性格使然，我內心更大的聲音是反抗但我又想啊，跟一群理念不同的人吵，又有何意義呢？8月6日的香港，也是亂成一團相信各位都在微博上看到很多很多言論和視頻那一晚我徹夜未眠決定在朋友圈抒發一下，我是這樣說的:<br />\n<a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-37924edea23cbd618b81a1593bffed5f_hd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-37924edea23cbd618b81a1593bffed5f_hd.jpg&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=3e3e6fc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-37924edea23cbd618b81a1593bffed5f_hd.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4673c337cb4ce92deae474db2f642276_hd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-4673c337cb4ce92deae474db2f642276_hd.jpg&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=ee004945\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4673c337cb4ce92deae474db2f642276_hd.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-78753991426047e75f49ecaf3c94c96d_hd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-78753991426047e75f49ecaf3c94c96d_hd.jpg&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=f3a3b5ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-78753991426047e75f49ecaf3c94c96d_hd.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f17ee6eb545054809a0dc0c7abe3f8c1_hd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-f17ee6eb545054809a0dc0c7abe3f8c1_hd.jpg&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=34790d9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f17ee6eb545054809a0dc0c7abe3f8c1_hd.jpg</a><br />\n經過這一夜我決定不再時時刻刻關注着因爲我厭倦，我恨我自己無能為力，我感到很愧疚傳媒的偏頗，社交平台的大數據影響之下假若你不跳出那框架，只會看到自己所看和*他*想讓你看的因此我專注自己的學業，工作，愛好我努力經營我的古方護膚品小店，學習更多現代的技術，做不同實驗，將古方原素融入進去我努力經營生活，過好每一天我努力讀書，希望將來可以幫助到更多人我堅決不讓他們的所作所為，去掌握着我的生活！付哥哥的舉行，是我覺得男人該有的樣子那群人，示威者？暴徒？黑衣人？喜歡怎麼說就怎麼說吧正如我在朋友圈所說已不再是常人所為矛頭指向錯方，自己人打自己人最近所發生的事，歷史上也有經歷過香港，一群壞的人帶着一群蠢的人去做壞事我愛中國，感恩在此看到世界的美好感恩我學有所成感恩這個國家讓我改變了很多固有思維香港，是我出生地現在剩下的，就只能好好努力改變，重回正軌吧因爲愛，所以我無怨無悔最後，衷心希望付哥哥早日康復感謝您<br />\n<br />\n作者：Kristy<br />\n链接：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050/answer/787573452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F340424050%2Fanswer%2F787573452&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=7e91baed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050/answer/787573452</a><br />\n来源：知乎<br />\n著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時去光復知乎</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8fa7747987945d3eaf0788d99576a02f24bddfbe","tid":1470229,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-37924edea23cbd618b81a1593bffed5f_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-37924edea23cbd618b81a1593bffed5f_hd.jpg&h=7c460ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4673c337cb4ce92deae474db2f642276_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-4673c337cb4ce92deae474db2f642276_hd.jpg&h=e5120200&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-78753991426047e75f49ecaf3c94c96d_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-78753991426047e75f49ecaf3c94c96d_hd.jpg&h=0f7128a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f17ee6eb545054809a0dc0c7abe3f8c1_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-f17ee6eb545054809a0dc0c7abe3f8c1_hd.jpg&h=dfcd5684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"235ce45545ca4c68bdd6ee2e8937b3e7ba29cc0b","tid":1470229,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2306836171f86ba8ea75012b6abefbc537b76e1b","tid":1470229,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"推乜鳩丫<br />\n睇完頭兩行已經唔駛睇啦，邊個指鹿為馬大家心裡有數啦，仲話認賊作父就好明顯講緊抗爭緊既市民。<br />\n<br />\n知乎出左名係政治正確，佢選擇得係入面出post就即係話佢唔驚河蟹，人地打算圍爐你去理佢做乜？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲言論睇都浪費時間，咁鍾意做狗就唔好強調自己係香港人啦，話自己係護旗手同中國人咪仲多大陸仔讚好"},{"pid":"35bd20ebfff3bb8081696a259467cd8f44ee1187","tid":1470229,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔駛推post啦，帝吧做果的垃圾行為唔駛follow"}]}